Package com.i2group.apollo.alertfeedretrievalservice.transport

Contains classes for the service that retrieves alert feeds from the Analysis Repository.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AlertFeedInfo Information that describes an alert feed to a client, including the ItemIdentifier of the feed, the ItemIdentifier of the Item (or ItemPlaceholder) being monitored, and an indication of how the current user receives alerts from the feed.
AlertFeedSearchResults Contains the AlertFeedInfos and other information that form the results of a search for alert feeds.
